Class ConfigManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.peyrona.mingle.glue.ConfigManager
  • public final class ConfigManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Centralized configuration manager for Glue application. This class consolidates all configuration data that was previously stored in separate files into a single JSON configuration file.
